<paragraph lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="89" pageId="3" pageNumber="88">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="88">Female genitalia</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 12–16" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 12 - 16. Female genitalia of Cochylis spp. 12 Cochylis atricapitana (Stephens), slide No. SYH 11456 13 Cochylis discerta Razowski, slide No. SYH 11573 14 Cochylis faustana (Kennel), slide No. SYH 10228 15 Cochylis posterana hyrcana (Toll), slide No. SYH 11445 16 Cochylis triangula sp. n., paratype, slide No. SYH 11700. (scales: 0.5 mm)." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27130" pageId="3" pageNumber="88">Fig. 13</figureCitation>
